{"tid":148063,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Lilian Kan：胸部線條是變飽滿，也更有彈性","createTime":"2017-03-08T10:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T16:28:32.000Z","uid":35468,"like":22,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bdb0de64eaf20097fb3aee7f6681a8745fbdce3","tid":148063,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"這個我也考慮了一會，好不好分享呢？<br />\n我很怕女生們看到這個POST會覺得，<br />\n「對吧，大胸才是好&hellip;」，<br />\n比起大小，我其實比較著重線條，<br />\n肌膚的彈性和質感。<br />\n不要羨慕別人擁有什麼，<br />\n因為自己的身體才是跟著自己一輩子的。<br />\n我們女生其實都是因為愛錫自己的身體，<br />\n才會想努力保養，<br />\n我也覺得努力去保養自己<br />\n每一吋肌膚的女人很美。<br />\n有些人會覺得，還是保守點有氣質，<br />\n我倒是覺得，這個年代，<br />\n談吐待人接物才是重點，<br />\n性感點就等於想要「別人埋單」<br />\n或是引誘異性的，<br />\n也不免有點守舊。<br />\n好了，我想說，<br />\n這些吃下去的東東我不敢隨便推薦，<br />\n我自己先試了一個月。<br />\nPueraria美胸膠囊中的effective ingredient <br />\n是大豆異黃酮，<br />\n平日飲食中天然食品如豆漿、<br />\n豆腐、黃豆、杏仁等種籽和堅果類都<br />\n含豐富大豆異黃酮，<br />\n是可以調節雌激素的分泌的好東西，<br />\n但有時飲食不一定每天都很均衡，<br />\n所以對美胸來說，是很好的小幫手，<br />\n除了美胸之外，雌激素還有其他好處，<br />\n幫助月經按時來，也令肌膚細緻柔軟。<br />\n真實體驗呢？<br />\n配合葛根美胸啫喱在洗澡後按摩使用，<br />\n可以令肌膚更容易吸收，<br />\n沒有什麼誇張的變大效果，<br />\n但胸部線條是真的有變飽滿，也更有彈性，<br />\n而使用在身體各部位則令線條更firm。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15J55RL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15J55RL.jpg&h=561400c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6TNU7OS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6TNU7OS.jpg&h=4f8f5207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&lt;iframe src=&quot;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flilian.kan%2Fposts%2F10158414436315165&amp;width=500&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Flilian.kan%252Fposts%252F10158414436315165%26width%3D500%22&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d4910960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flilian.kan%2Fposts%2F10158414436315165&amp;width=500&quot;</a> width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;693&quot; style=&quot;border:none;overflow:hidden&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowTransparency=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;"},{"pid":"26a1e33ff87c0809385d9c1a27923ec178344365","tid":148063,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lilian.kan/posts/10158414436315165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flilian.kan%2Fposts%2F10158414436315165&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7db7ca11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lilian.kan/posts/10158414436315165</a>"},{"pid":"8996a68b15d4514b9ee1396f14b47d51bcd455e6","tid":148063,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"飲多D豆漿都OK"},{"pid":"701e2253b860e73aadf8cad3387e6b74d45ed684","tid":148063,"uid":6557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:17:20.000Z","msg":"妖, 佢本身都有波, 你搵阿sa代言有成效我就服啦"},{"pid":"253551b1e16f08ddf67372b75d44beb7a39bca1e","tid":148063,"uid":45766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:26:51.000Z","msg":"好撚正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96743a804d2f6bcb085e0a5dc3d2b0263026c509","tid":148063,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:30:44.000Z","msg":"幻想到佢沖涼吱d啫喱落手 然後慢慢打圈咁捽對波 又彈又白滑 動L動L咁 嘩諗起到扯到行哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc4b249a2360a43fa6fdba3fec03d115911fc2a","tid":148063,"uid":36316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"咪又係雞"},{"pid":"cbd21ae9d1537a3dad329ca65628be0a564dd2ad","tid":14806